text: Komarovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Nikolo-Komarovsky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 354 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 41 km WNW from Kamyzyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Komarovka
